  • The smoothie bowl maker that blends and powers through for spoon-thick smoothie bowls

  • (2) 24-oz. Ninja Nutrient Extraction Cups with (2) Spout Lids
  • Version B Bullet 6
  • 4 preset Auto-iQ programs: Smoothie, Extract, Bowl, and Spread
  • 2 manual programs

  • Recipe inspiration guide

Kohl's Cookies

When you visit any website, it may store or retrieve information on your browser, mostly in the form of cookies. This information might be about you, your preferences or your device and is mostly used to make the site work as you expect it to. The information does not usually directly identify you, but it can give you a more personalized web experience. Under law, California and Virginia residents have the right to tell us not to sell their personal information. At Kohls, the only sales we make (as defined by Applicable law) are to share certain information among our affiliates consisting of cookies stored on your browser to provide more relevant ads to you on our sites, apps, and on other sites that you visit. On this page you can choose not to allow some types of cookies. Click on the different category headings to find out more and change the default settings. However, blocking some types of cookies may impact your experience of the site and the services we are able to offer.

Required Cookies

Always Active

These cookies are necessary for the website to function and cannot be switched off in our systems. They are usually only set in response to actions made by you which amount to a request for services, such as setting your privacy preferences, logging in or filling in forms. You can set your browser to block or alert you about these cookies, but some parts of the site will not work. These cookies do not store any personally identifiable information.

Sale or Sharing of Personal Information (including Targeted Advertising)

At Kohls, the only "sharing" or sales we make (as defined by applicable law) is the sharing of certain customer online information among our affiliates consisting of cookies stored on your browser to provide more relevant ads to you on our sites, apps, and on other sites that you visit. If youd like us not to sell or "share" this information, then please disable this use of your data with our third parties on this tab. To Opt-In to the sale or sharing (including targeted advertising) of your personal information, please ensure that the toggle above is to the RIGHT and BLUE. In the alternative, to Opt-Out of the sale or sharing (including targeted advertising) of your personal information, please ensure that the toggle above is to the LEFT and GRAY
